description:
Australia is blue around its edges and red in its center. The coasts are densely populated but the center has a treasure trove of beauty and wonder to offer. This week we will explore the fascinating treasures of this barren heartland. Will look at the scorching red plains of Australias desert heartland and a message of love the hand of God has written for each of us in this stunning landscape.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheIncredibleJourneyMinistry/
